{
    "attributes": {
        "action": " Redirect some foreign aid to fund services for British children",
        "additional_details": "We are concerned by the years of cuts that UK children\u2019s services have faced. Meanwhile, \u00a318 billion has been allocated to Ukraine, including military and humanitarian aid. We believe children in the UK deserve focused support, especially those growing up in working-class communities or facing mental health struggles. We are asking for a fairer distribution of public funds to support British children.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to redirect a portion of overseas aid\u2014particularly the \u00a318 billion already committed to Ukraine\u2014toward supporting the future of British children.",
